# ── NSE Swing Screener — Environment Variables ────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Copy this file and rename it  .env
# 2. Fill in your values below
# 3. NEVER commit the .env file to git (it contains your password)
#
# HOW TO GET A GMAIL APP PASSWORD
# ────────────────────────────────
# a) Go to  https://myaccount.google.com/security
# b) Enable 2-Step Verification (required)
# c) Go to  https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# d) Select app: "Mail"  |  device: "Windows Computer"
# e) Google will show you a 16-character password — paste it below
#    (no spaces, all lowercase)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Your Gmail address (the account that sends the alert)
GMAIL_SENDER=shastritilak880@gmail.com

# The 16-character App Password Google generates (NOT your Gmail login password)
GMAIL_APP_PASS=spgyqdcjuafkmkmr

# Comma-separated list of email addresses that receive the alerts.
# Add as many as you want. No spaces around the comma.
ALERT_RECIPIENTS=shastritilak880@gmail.com,bsbstktrading@gmail.com
